@node "IMPORTANT" "IMPORTANT NOTE"
*** IMPORTANT NOTE ***

Make sure to use the PhoneBook of Quickdial menu to dial a BBS since the NEW
Multimedia commands will not function properly and pictures/sounds will not be
downloaded!  Also file transfer ratios and origions can not be recorded in
this way.

This means that you should not manually type ATDT01752 366939 or use the 'Dial
#' option to dial a BBS even if it is in the Phone Book since it will not be
reconised.  These options only real use is for quickly checking out a BBS or
calling a friend without a BBS.
@endnode

